title: [Whistler's Pass, Creek]
description: The flow of the creek has cut its path in the sandstone that lines this section of the creek bed.  Fireflies flutter through the area, the braver ones inspecting trespassers to their nighttime resting spot.
The flow of the creek has cut its path in the sandstone that lines this section of the creek bed.  Dragonflies flutter through the area, the braver ones inspecting trespassers to their territory.
